10	 * Implementation strategy: each op performs line surgery on the tree, then
11	 * the canonical result is parse(encode(surgery)) — closure with the mapping
12	 * holds by construction, and the inverse-law tests guard semantics.
13	 *
14	 * Markdown-imposed rejections beyond the bounds:
15	 * - content cannot become a *sibling of a heading section it is inside*
16	 *   (heading scope is positional), so outdent out of a heading is rejected;
17	 * - only list items can nest under a paragraph, and nothing nests under an
